name: Lady Pac
overview: Lady Pac is a maze game for the Commodore 64. It is a homage to Ms. Pac-Man, an arcade game published by Midway in 1982. Main differences from the original version: • Randomly generated mazes • Bonus rounds The game works perfectly on both PAL and NTSC models. However, for game speeds similar to the original arcade game, it is suggested using an NTSC model.
